      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。关于分支的显示顺序，您希望feature_1在main左侧，feature_2在main右侧吗？另外commit标签需要显示出来吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "branch order",
        "showCommitLabel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，feature_1放左边order 0，main保持order 1，feature_2放右边order 2。commit标签要显示，方便追踪每个节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "feature_1 order: 0",
        "main order: 1",
        "feature_2 order: 2",
        "showCommitLabel: true"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先搭建基础结构：main上提交a，然后分出两条分支。feature_1先切过去做提交f，然后回到main做提交b，这样交替进行。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit a",
        "branch feature_1",
        "branch feature_2",
        "commit f",
        "commit b"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来的提交顺序要注意：feature_1上继续g和h，feature_2上做u和v，两条分支独立推进，最后一起合并回main。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit g",
        "commit h",
        "commit u",
        "commit v",
        "merge feature_1",
        "merge feature_2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下流程：切到feature_1做g，然后feature_2做u，再切回feature_1做h，feature_2做v，最后main先后合并feature_1和feature_2。对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout sequence",
        "merge order"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，就是这个顺序。还有，麻烦把调试级别设成debug，方便有问题时检查，主题用base保持简洁。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "logLevel: debug",
        "theme: base"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。主干和两条特性分支的并行开发流程已经画好，分支左右对称，所有commit标签清晰可见，最后两个merge节点都指向main。",
